                <![CDATA[<p>Google 推出的 Android 「画圈搜寻」（Circle to Search）功能，让 Android 手机用户可以以画圈方式直接搜寻。现在 iPhone 用家也可以使用类似功能，只需使用 iOS 版最新的 Google app 搭配 Google 以图搜图捷径即可。</p><p>Google 今年一月推出了「Circle to Search」，用户无须再跳转至搜寻引擎，可以直接在萤幕以画圈手势搜寻图片及文字。现在 iPhone 用家也可以使用类似功能，要使用这个功能，首先你要下载最新的「Google」应用程式，随后再安装「捷径」，简单设定后无论在网上或是在现实生活中遇到有趣的事，也可以直接使用「以图搜寻」功能上网搜寻。</p><h2>Step 1 下载／更新 Google 应用程式</h2><p>要在 iPhone 使用「画圈搜寻」功能，首先要安装／更新 Google 应用程式。下载连结：<a href="https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/google/id284815942">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/google/id284815942</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239082" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716969059-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716969059-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716969059.jpeg 369w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><h2>Step 2 允许「Google」App 存取照片</h2><p>下载完成后，开启 Google 应用程式，点击下图绿色框指住的按键，允许 Google 存取你的图片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239122" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1-1-2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1-1-2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/1-1-2.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击上图框住的按键</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239123" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-6-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-6-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-6.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「Allow access」</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239120" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169722332-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169722332-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169722332.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「允许全权取用」</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/22/pairdrop/software/android-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】跨平台无线传送档案，不在家 Android、iOS 传相片影片到家中电脑</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/apple-to-allow-iphones-to-function-as-my-number-cards-japan/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">日本身份证将加入 Apple 钱包，美国以外首个国家支援</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/28/iphone-22/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中国 4 月 iPhone 销量增 52%    智能手机销量按年增长 25.5%</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>Step 3 下载「捷径」</h2><p>下载完 Google 应用程式后，此时要安装 Apple 官方「捷径」应用程式（<a href="https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E6%8D%B7%E5%BE%91/id915249334">下载连结</a>）。如果你的电话已经有这个 App，就可以跳至 Step 4。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239087" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240529155449-681x580.jpg" alt="" width="681" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240529155449-681x580.jpg 681w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240529155449.jpg 1056w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 681px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲没有「捷径」的用家可以先下载这个 Apple 官方应用程式</p><h2>Step 4 设定「捷径」</h2><p>安装完成后开启捷径，然后点击右上角的「<b>+</b>」符号，跳页后按「加入动作」，在「搜寻 App 和动作」位置输入「Take screenshot」，选择「拍摄萤幕截图」。接下来再次在「搜寻 App 和动作」输入「Google」，点击</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239127" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/3-5-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/3-5-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/3-5.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「+」符号（绿框示）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239129" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/4-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/4-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/4-1.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「加入动作」符号（绿框示）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239133" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/5-2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/5-2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/5-2.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在绿色框处输入「Take screenshot」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239131" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169722335-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169722335-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169722335.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「拍摄萤幕截图」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239136" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/6-2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/6-2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/6-2.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在此栏目输入「Google」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239137" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/7-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/7-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/7-1.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击绿色框框住的 Google 字样</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239156" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/8-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/8-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/8-1.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「使用智慧镜头搜寻图片」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239157" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/9-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/9-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/9.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「完成」（绿色框示）</p><h2>Step 4 设定快速开启「画圈搜寻」功能</h2><p>倘若要每次开启「捷径」才能使用这个功能的话，略嫌有点不方便。要如 Android 般一键使用「画圈搜寻」，我们可以使用 iPhone 的辅助触控功能，点击手机后背 2 下即可自动启用「画圈搜寻」功能。先开启设定，选择「辅助使用」，选择「触控」，然后点击「机背点按」，选择「使用智慧镜头搜寻图片」，之后你就可以轻拍机背 2 下召唤「画圈搜寻」功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239168" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716976552-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716976552-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716976552.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲开启「设定」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239170" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/10-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/10-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/10.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「辅助使用」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239171" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/11-1-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/11-1-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/11-1-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/11-1.png 591w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「触控」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239174" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/12-2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/12-2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/12-2.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「机背点按」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239176" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/13-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/13-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/13-1.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「使用智慧镜头搜寻图片」</p><p style="text-align: center;"> </p><h2>Step 5 完成</h2><p>现时已完成所有设定，如果你在上网时看到感兴趣的图片，可以轻点机背 2 下，即可召唤「画圈搜寻」功能。</p><div style="padding: 216.22% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_2548" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/951470981?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p>如果你想直接拍摄照片，再利用 Google 智慧镜头搜寻，这个捷径也能够帮到你。首先开启「相机」，对准你要搜寻的物品，然后轻点机背 2 下，这样就可以使用捷径搜寻你镜头拍摄的物品。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239218" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716981245-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716981245-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo1716981245.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲开启相机镜头后轻点机背 2 下</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239219" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169812451-268x580.jpeg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169812451-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/photo17169812451.jpeg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲即可搜寻相机拍摄到的图片</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/22/pairdrop/software/android-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】跨平台无线传送档案，不在家 Android、iOS 传相片影片到家中电脑</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/apple-to-allow-iphones-to-function-as-my-number-cards-japan/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">日本身份证将加入 Apple 钱包，美国以外首个国家支援</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/28/iphone-22/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中国 4 月 iPhone 销量增 52%    智能手机销量按年增长 25.5%</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>总结：前期设定较为繁复　使用非常方便</h2><p>虽然这个捷径前期设定步骤比较繁复，但小编觉得这个捷径算是实用，上网时只要看见感兴趣的东西，轻点机背 2 下即可搜寻；开启相机时点击机背 2 下亦可直接 Google 搜寻相机拍摄到的画面。</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/22/pairdrop/software/android-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】跨平台无线传送档案，不在家 Android、iOS 传相片影片到家中电脑</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/31/apple-to-allow-iphones-to-function-as-my-number-cards-japan/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">日本身份证将加入 Apple 钱包，美国以外首个国家支援</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/28/iphone-22/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">中国 4 月 iPhone 销量增 52%    智能手机销量按年增长 25.5%</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/30/iphone-circle-to-search-by-shortcut/tips-2/">【教学】iPhone 也可「画圈搜寻」　轻触机背即可使用 + 即影即 Google</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
